            "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1032280/extras/Banner_Voice-Controlled_small.png?t=1551143658\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Requirements</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Currently only playable with Windows 10!</strong><br></li><li>Headset/Microphone (no keyboard/controller needed, voice-operated!) </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Game</h2><br><strong><i>The Voice Inside</i></strong> is an innovative <strong>voice-controlled psychological horror game</strong>, that takes you on a journey deep down into your heart, mind &amp; soul.<br>Command your character through different paths to find the &quot;Inner Values&quot;, by using only your voice &amp; let the <strong><i>voice inside</i></strong> guide you to find your way out. <br>But be careful, the enemy is close - <i>Darkness</i> is chasing you!<br>Just listen, follow your intuition &amp; give the right commands to reach your goal!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Voice Commands</h2><br>Use a good <strong>headset or microphone </strong>&amp; speak loud and clear. Avoid loud background noises to make the speech recognition system work well.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Move (go/walk)</strong> – normal speed<br></li><li><strong>Hurry </strong>– let your character run <br></li><li><strong>Stop (wait/hold on)</strong> - stop the character immediately <br></li><li><strong>Sneak </strong> - slow movement to avoid the enemy’s attention <br></li><li><strong>Speed Up</strong> – increase your current speed<br></li><li><strong>Turn Right</strong> (right) – turns 90° right</li></ul><br>and many more...<br>Just listen to the voice inside. It tells you what to do.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1032280/extras/Header_ADK_TVI2_banner_tiny_roundCorners.png?t=1551143658\" >",
